(48, 3, 9, 48, 3, 14, 14, 'blessed with faithful Abraham', 'Connection of Faith and Blessing', 'Both passages emphasize the blessing associated with Abraham and the role of faith. The first verse highlights that those of faith are blessed with Abraham, while the second verse connects this blessing to the Gentiles through Jesus Christ.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 3, 9, 48, 3, 7, 8, 'blessed with faithful Abraham', 'Faith and Abraham''s Blessing', 'Both passages emphasize that those who have faith are considered children of Abraham and are blessed. This connection highlights the idea that faith is central to receiving God''s promise of blessing to all nations through Abraham.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
