(48, 3, 10, 45, 8, 7, 7, 'works of the law', 'Connection of Law and Mind', 'Both passages emphasize the inability to fulfill the law. Galatians highlights the curse for not adhering to the law, while Romans states that the carnal mind cannot be subject to it.', 'theme', 0.482, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
