(48, 3, 10, 24, 11, 3, 3, 'Cursed is every one that continueth not', 'Curses for Disobedience', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of curses for those who do not obey God''s commands. Galatians references the law, while Jeremiah speaks of the covenant, linking the consequences of disobedience in both contexts.', 'theme', 0.43299999999999994, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
