(48, 4, 6, 65, 1, 20, 20, NULL, 'Connection of Faith and Spirit', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the Holy Spirit in the lives of believers. Galatians highlights the Spirit of God''s Son in our hearts, while Jude encourages praying in the Holy Ghost, linking the believer''s identity and spiritual practice.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 7, 45, 8, 16, 17, 'heir of God through Christ', 'Connection of Heirs in Christ', 'Both passages emphasize the status of believers as heirs of God through their relationship with Christ. They highlight the transition from being servants to being recognized as children of God, which carries the promise of inheritance.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 7, 46, 3, 21, 23, 'heir of God through Christ', 'Inheritance and Belonging', 'This connection highlights the theme of believers'' identity as heirs and their belonging to Christ. Both passages emphasize the idea that being a son or belonging to Christ grants access to all things, reinforcing the notion of spiritual inheritance.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
