(48, 4, 7, 19, 73, 26, 26, 'heir of God through Christ', 'Connection of Inheritance and Strength', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of God as a source of strength and inheritance. In Galatians, being an heir of God signifies a deep relationship, while in Psalms, God is described as the strength and portion of the heart.', 'theme', 0.356, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 7, 47, 6, 16, 18, NULL, 'Sonship and Divine Relationship', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of believers as children of God. In Galatians, being a son makes one an heir, while in 2 Corinthians, God promises to be a Father to His people, highlighting their identity as sons and daughters.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 7, 25, 3, 24, 24, 'no more a servant, but a son', 'Hope in God''s Provision', 'This connection highlights the theme of belonging and assurance in God. Both passages emphasize the relationship between the believer and God, portraying the believer as a son and an heir, which fosters hope in God''s provision.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 8, 46, 8, 4, 4, 'which by nature are no gods', 'Idols and True God', 'This connection highlights the concept of idols as false deities. Both passages emphasize the idea that those who do not know God serve entities that are not true gods.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 8, 49, 2, 11, 12, NULL, 'Connection of Gentiles and God', 'Both passages emphasize the state of being ''without God'' and the service to false gods. They highlight the spiritual condition of Gentiles before knowing God, illustrating their separation from the promises and hope found in Christ.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 8, 52, 1, 9, 9, 'service unto them which by nature are no gods', 'Turning from Idols to God', 'Both passages emphasize the transition from serving false gods to serving the true God. Galatians mentions service to those which are no gods, while 1 Thessalonians highlights turning to God from idols.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
