(48, 4, 10, 45, 14, 5, 5, 'days, and months, and times, and years', 'Observance of Days and Times', 'This connection highlights the differing attitudes towards the observance of days. Both passages emphasize the importance of personal conviction in how one regards specific days.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
