(48, 4, 10, 3, 25, 13, 13, 'days, and months, and times, and years', 'Observance of Time and Seasons', 'This connection highlights the significance of specific time periods in both passages. Galatians mentions observing ''days, and months, and times, and years,'' while Leviticus refers to the ''year of this jubile,'' emphasizing the importance of designated times for returning to one''s possessions.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(48, 4, 10, 4, 28, 1, 29, 'observe days, and months, and times', 'Observance of Sacred Times', 'This connection highlights the emphasis on observing specific times and offerings in both passages. Galatians 4:10 mentions the observance of days, months, and years, while Numbers 28:1-29 details the offerings to be made at these appointed times.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
