(48, 4, 11, 46, 15, 58, 58, 'labour in vain', 'Labor in Vain Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of labor and its value in the Christian faith. Both passages address the concern of labor being in vain, with Galatians expressing fear of such a reality and Corinthians affirming that labor in the Lord is not in vain.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
