(48, 4, 28, 44, 3, 25, 25, 'children of promise', 'Children of Promise and Covenant', 'This connection highlights the theme of being ''children'' linked to God''s promises. Both passages emphasize the relationship of believers to Abraham''s covenant and the blessings that flow from it.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
