(48, 4, 30, 48, 3, 8, 8, 'son of the bondwoman shall not be heir', 'Connection of Heirs and Blessings', 'This connection highlights the theme of inheritance and blessing. Both passages address the distinction between those who are heirs through faith and those who are not, emphasizing God''s promise to bless all nations through Abraham.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
