(48, 5, 2, 48, 5, 6, 6, NULL, 'Circumcision and Faith Connection', 'This connection highlights the futility of circumcision in relation to faith in Christ. Both passages emphasize that neither circumcision nor uncircumcision holds value, but rather faith working through love is what truly matters.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
